        "postTitle": "SaRa Lifestyle opens 17th outlet in Narsingdi",
        "postDescription": "<p style=\"border: 0 solid; margin-bottom: 1.5em; color: rgba(40, 48, 59, 1); font-family: \"IBM Plex Serif\", serif; font-size: 17px\"><span style=\"border: 0 solid; margin: 0; padding: 0; font-weight: bolder\">Bangladeshi fashion retail brand SaRa Lifestyle has opened its 17th outlet in Narsingdi.</span></p><p style=\"border: 0 solid; margin-bottom: 1.5em; color: rgba(40, 48, 59, 1); font-family: \"IBM Plex Serif\", serif; font-size: 17px\"><span style=\"border: 0 solid; margin: 0; padding: 0; font-weight: bolder\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">The inauguration took place on March 5 at Boakur Mor in the town, says a press release.</span></span></p><p style=\"border: 0 solid; margin-bottom: 1.5em; color: rgba(40, 48, 59, 1); font-family: \"IBM Plex Serif\", serif; font-size: 17px\">Mosharrof Hossain, director of Snowtex Group, Md. Faizur Rahman Nuri, deputy director of Snowtex Group, Shakib Ahsan, DGM and head of operations at SaRa Lifestyle, AGM Apurbo Goshami, and Faraz Hossain Rumman, head of brand and communications, were present at the event.</p><p style=\"border: 0 solid; margin-bottom: 1.5em; color: rgba(40, 48, 59, 1); font-family: \"IBM Plex Serif\", serif; font-size: 17px\">Speaking at the programme, Mosharrof Hossain said the company was pleased to launch a new showroom in Narsingdi.</p><p style=\"border: 0 solid; margin-bottom: 1.5em; color: rgba(40, 48, 59, 1); font-family: \"IBM Plex Serif\", serif; font-size: 17px\">He said SaRa Lifestyle began its journey with the vision of building a brand in Bangladesh where customers can find quality, modern design and reliability under one roof.</p><p style=\"border: 0 solid; margin-bottom: 1.5em; color: rgba(40, 48, 59, 1); font-family: \"IBM Plex Serif\", serif; font-size: 17px\">“With the launch of this new showroom in Narsingdi, we aim to get closer to our customers and offer them a shopping experience built on care, style and trust,” he said.</p><p style=\"border: 0 solid; margin-bottom: 1.5em; color: rgba(40, 48, 59, 1); font-family: \"IBM Plex Serif\", serif; font-size: 17px\">He added that the brand hopes to attract customers through quality products at affordable prices while maintaining strict quality control and ensuring the best possible customer support.</p><p style=\"border: 0 solid; margin-bottom: 1.5em; color: rgba(40, 48, 59, 1); font-family: \"IBM Plex Serif\", serif; font-size: 17px\">SaRa Lifestyle offers winter wear including jackets. The brand combines local heritage with contemporary fashion trends and provides clothing for young professionals, students and families.</p><p style=\"border: 0 solid; margin-bottom: 1.5em; color: rgba(40, 48, 59, 1); font-family: \"IBM Plex Serif\", serif; font-size: 17px\">With the opening of the new outlet at Boakur Mor in Narsingdi, customers in the area will have access to SaRa Lifestyle’s winter wear and jacket collections.</p><p style=\"border: 0 solid; margin-bottom: 1.5em; color: rgba(40, 48, 59, 1); font-family: \"IBM Plex Serif\", serif; font-size: 17px\">Customers will receive a flat 15 percent discount on all products from March 5 to March 7 to mark the opening.</p><p style=\"border: 0 solid; margin-bottom: 1.5em; color: rgba(40, 48, 59, 1); font-family: \"IBM Plex Serif\", serif; font-size: 17px\">The outlet offers clothing for men, women and children. It also includes a kids’ play zone.</p><p style=\"border: 0 solid; margin-bottom: 1.5em; color: rgba(40, 48, 59, 1); font-family: \"IBM Plex Serif\", serif; font-size: 17px\">The outlet also offers collections from SaRa Lifestyle’s western sub-brand “DHEU”, designed for young consumers.</p><p style=\"border: 0 solid; margin-bottom: 1.5em; color: rgba(40, 48, 59, 1); font-family: \"IBM Plex Serif\", serif; font-size: 17px\">SaRa Lifestyle now operates 17 outlets along with an e-commerce platform.</p><div style=\"border: 0 solid; margin: 0 0 20px; padding: 0; color: rgba(40, 48, 59, 1); font-family: \"IBM Plex Serif\", serif; font-size: 17px\"><div id=\"js-dfp-tag-en_photo_banner\" style=\"border: 0 solid; margin: 0; padding: 0\"></div></div>",
