        "postTitle": "SaraLifestyle celebrates seventh anniversary",
        "postDescription": "<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 20px; text-align: justify; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1); font-family: \"FF Meta Serif Pro\"; background-color: rgba(254, 254, 254, 1)\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: 700; line-height: inherit\">Popular fashion brand SaAa Lifestyle Limited has completed seven years of its journey.</span></p><div id=\"div-ub-tbsnews.net_1706867223147\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1); font-family: \"FF Meta Serif Pro\"; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgba(254, 254, 254, 1)\"></div><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 20px; text-align: justify; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1); font-family: \"FF Meta Serif Pro\"; background-color: rgba(254, 254, 254, 1)\">Launched in 2018, the brand has quickly established a special place in the hearts of fashion-conscious consumers nationwide.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 20px; text-align: justify; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1); font-family: \"FF Meta Serif Pro\"; background-color: rgba(254, 254, 254, 1)\">A proud local clothing brand of apparel manufacturer and exporter, Snowtex Group, SaRa was founded with a clear mission — to offer quality fashion at affordable prices. Staying true to that goal, the brand has become a trusted name among shoppers nationwide.<br><br>To mark its anniversary, SaRa has announced a series of exciting campaigns, including a picture contest, a \"Buy One, Get One\" offer, and a quiz competition.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 20px; text-align: justify; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1); font-family: \"FF Meta Serif Pro\"; background-color: rgba(254, 254, 254, 1)\">As part of the picture contest, anyone can participate by uploading a photo of themselves wearing SaRa's clothing on the brand's official Facebook page to win attractive prizes. The \"Buy One, Get One\" offer allows customers to purchase a second selected item for just Tk 7 when a minimum purchase of Tk 1,000 is made. The quiz competition also promises exciting rewards for winners.</p><div style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0 0 1rem; padding: 0; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1); font-family: \"FF Meta Serif Pro\"; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgba(254, 254, 254, 1)\"><div id=\"dfp-ad-tbs_rectangle_snd_mobile-wrapper\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0\"></div></div><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 20px; text-align: justify; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1); font-family: \"FF Meta Serif Pro\"; background-color: rgba(254, 254, 254, 1)\">Demonstrating its commitment to social responsibility, SaRa has planted 700 trees along the banks of Kadamtoli Lake in Gulshan, Dhaka. The brand believes the initiative will play a meaningful role in preserving nature and improving the environment. SaRa has also pledged to continue such efforts in the future.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 20px; text-align: justify; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1); font-family: \"FF Meta Serif Pro\"; background-color: rgba(254, 254, 254, 1)\">Sharifun Reba, Director of Snowtex Group and SaRa Lifestyle, shared, \"Over the past seven years, we've been truly grateful to our customers, partners, and team. Their unwavering support and love have inspired us every step of the way. We remain committed to bringing even better experiences in the days ahead.\"</p><div style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0 0 1rem; padding: 0; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1); font-family: \"FF Meta Serif Pro\"; font-size: 20px; background-color: rgba(254, 254, 254, 1)\"><div id=\"dfp-ad-tbs_rectangle_snd_mobile02-wrapper\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0; padding: 0\"></div></div><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 20px; text-align: justify; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1); font-family: \"FF Meta Serif Pro\"; background-color: rgba(254, 254, 254, 1)\">Founded in May 2018, a sister concern of Snowtex Group, SaRa opened its first outlet in Mirpur-6, Dhaka, followed by a second store at Bashundhara City (Level 1, Block A, Shop 40 and 54). Since then, the brand has expanded to key locations including Mohammadpur (Ring Road, Block F), Uttara (House 22, Sonargaon Janapath, Sector 9), Baridhara (J Block), Banasree (E Block, Road 1), Wari (Rankin Street), Rangpur (Jahaj Company Mor), Rajshahi (United Tower, Rani Bazar), Basabo (East Basabo, Sabujbagh), Bogura (City Center, Jaleshwari Tola), Sylhet (VIP Road, Kumarpara), Feni (Ohab Tower), Barishal (Bibir Pukur Par, Fakir Complex, Sadar Road), Narayanganj (TNS Plaza, Bangabandhu Road), with plans to launch a new outlet soon at Shibbari Mor, Khulna.</p>",
