        "postDescription": "<p style=\"text-align:start;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(16,24,40);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 18px;font-family: Noto Serif JP\", serif;\">Keeping summer in mind, Sara Lifestyle has brought their Eid ul Azha collection. The designs have been made keeping the climate in mind. The designs feature screen print, embroidery, tie n' dye, etc. The selection of fabric includes cotton, synthetic fabrics, and silk. </span> <br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(16,24,40);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 18px;font-family: Noto Serif JP\", serif;\">The collection includes a wide of products for men, women, and children. The price range is affordable and kept between Tk 500 and 5000.</span> <br><br><span style=\"color: rgb(16,24,40);background-color: rgb(255,255,255);font-size: 18px;font-family: Noto Serif JP\", serif;\">The entire Eid ul Azha Collection is available at all their outlets. <br><br>Source: The Daily Star</span></p>\n",
